# thoth_policy_change_artifact_apply

Applies a generated policy change artifact through an approved apply channel.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "thoth_policy_change_artifact_apply" "crm_export_apply" {
  request_id       = thoth_policy_exception.crm_export.request_id
  applied_by       = "usec-ops"
  apply_channel    = "govapi"
  policy_format    = "rego"
  bundle_name      = "exception-crm-export"
  bundle_description = "Policy exception rollout for CRM export"
  assignments      = ["all"]
  enforcement_mode = "enforce"
  status           = "active"
}
```
